{"tid":1312232,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"欣宜首救命歌聽到好有共鳴","createTime":"2019-07-13T12:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:59:45.000Z","uid":256585,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0e211e348e93747b6e2fd2a9adfee4fcf76a8a95","tid":1312232,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hEsKDGxR7YE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhEsKDGxR7YE&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=b93eb4cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hEsKDGxR7YE</a><br />\n<br />\n好想一喝會飲醉 好想一瞓會死去<br />\n好想不去探討過活有幾累<br />\n不想觸碰那心碎 如提起都算種罪<br />\n毫無權利打攪誰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭先聽到呢幾句歌詞好似一刀一刀插入心口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起太古烈士佢地壯烈犧牲咗 <br />\n<br />\n接二連三一個跟住一個<br />\n<br />\n但係政府都叫天不應 真係好難過<br />\n<br />\n好愛香港但係真係好挫敗<br />\n<br />\n所以我同屋企都決定移民<br />\n<br />\n希望你地都會醒覺 you are not alone!<br />\n<br />\n有事記得嗌救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bc77ccc8ac81e89f80cdc2c6d622ace9116078","tid":1312232,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c28e677a9dcbe3ee113d4cb9e3a3f05d7d2e7c71","tid":1312232,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0615de320185e8a27265c76eaa0ca6850ec54bd5","tid":1312232,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"72ad3798df128a942d154475c19c9d13b0c953c7","tid":1312232,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3c670f032e2dbdde46d85d2f9172957f0fb389d","tid":1312232,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:32:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"30c46496a0aa1dd4a5102df79ce6f5280705241b","tid":1312232,"uid":256585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"如若你累到就快崩壞<br />\n人就算被困在無人地帶<br />\n不需驚醜怪<br />\n流淚自救<br />\n請將盔甲鬆懈<br />\n在懸崖盡處 仍舊記緊<br />\nLove is always inside"}]}